Description: Abseil random_internal_uniform_helper library
URL: https://abseil.io/
Version: 20260107
Requires: absl_config = 20260107, absl_random_internal_traits = 20260107, absl_type_traits = 20260107
Libs: -L${libdir}  
Cflags: -I${includedir} -DNOMINMAX
